{"tid":305016,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【呃人嘅！】3小時$1000愛國遊行 60人上當：車費都蝕埋","createTime":"2017-07-01T11:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T01:12:15.000Z","uid":12618,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dae75024d1e322ff57c5486d5a026d07ab2c42ac","tid":305016,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:00:27.000Z","msg":"年年遊行，都有不少愛國團體出錢出力「請人扮遊行」，今年亦不例外，8日前(23日)就有網友在LIHKG討論區的出post稱「遊行有錢收」，「七一愛國遊行，1,000蚊但淨係去3個鐘，可以戴口罩」，火速引起不少網民興趣。為了加強說服力，該網友更強調「2點至5點，可以戴口罩同黑超，有意者留低tg(手機app：Telegram)，名額有限。另外廢事有佔中黃屍玩野/記者放蛇，加左你之後會再double confirm，唔信就算！」<br />\n<br />\n中午1時半起，《蘋果》記者在天后站對出的維園入口，已發現一班青少年陸續抵達，其後聚集的人愈來愈多，高峰期達60人，當中不乏少女和大媽，但以青年人數較多，有小數人戴口罩、戴帽或黑超，幾乎全部人都一身便服，再配上波鞋，已做好遊行3小時的準備。惟最終眾人呆等2小時，出post的搞手仍未現身。<br />\n<br />\n其間陸續有參加者鼓譟及不滿道「等咗一個幾鐘，都唔出現，有無搞錯&hellip;&hellip;」、「叫得廢青，都知流啦」，當中更有參加者是特意由屯門出來，無奈表示「車費都蝕埋」。其中一名青年阿Mark稱，該名搞手自稱「fai Ching」(即廢青)，<span style=\"color: red;\">他日前在LIHKG討論區看到post，遂連同家人及朋友共6人報名，他笑言：「3小時就有1,000元非常筍！」惟等了2小時，搞手仍未現身，他邊看手邊說：「佢一直上線，但只讀不回。」</span><br />\n<br />\n阿Mark最後感到被騙，遂拉隊離開。自言政治中立的他坦言，自己是首次參加「收錢遊行」，只要有錢，不論黃絲藍絲都會參加，而日後亦會繼續參加，但會小心選擇，不再隨意參加網上的號召。事後，該名搞手在Telegram群組向參加者表示：「鑒於現場形勢對愛國活動十分不利，四周環境受到不同勢力嚴密鹽(監)控，為免參加者遇上混亂，現宣布活動取消。」<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊位巴打既好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445c001e94607533b0c03202f4d078150537d070","tid":305016,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"阿MARK真係典型貪錢港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff68f3d65dff10ba80c374bb235bb4d69d06a51","tid":305016,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/190639_199f7640b9d2f79c3f3973da1e2a38a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F190639_199f7640b9d2f79c3f3973da1e2a38a0.jpg&h=e3625786&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/190647_bc88b492aee5f402d245b65bc4e3a449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F190647_bc88b492aee5f402d245b65bc4e3a449.jpg&h=6610fa20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fee802e369a8aba9aba89658087169dd24ced6c","tid":305016,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"抵死，死傻閪"},{"pid":"21935e9e5ef90aaa998e55e108700440fa58378a","tid":305016,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"假膠都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf6a8eb267339d17e209554c820d4e582459088","tid":305016,"uid":19138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"成班傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac87cfe7ae02a323f4adf1cae6d9f53cc23360d3","tid":305016,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿MARK真係典型貪錢港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n釣港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f3c5362b8d2c8c8d2fa2d097b52a9e54b95d88","tid":305016,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/190639_1